<note style="-uslm-lc:I75" topic="referencesInText" id="id7a0d4e75-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">
<heading class="centered smallCaps">References in Text</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">This division, referred to in par. (2), is div. J of <ref href="/us/pl/117/263">Pub. L. 117–263</ref>, <date date="2022-12-23">Dec. 23, 2022</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/136/3930">136 Stat. 3930</ref>. For complete classification of div. J to the Code, see Tables.</p>
</note>
</notes>
</section>
